# ── Secrets (NEVER commit) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anything that looks like a wallet keypair, environment file, or worker state.
# If you add new private material, drop it under one of these paths.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/.secrets/
**/secrets/

# Any Solana keypair JSON anywhere in the tree. No exceptions — even program
# deploy keypairs (mainnet + devnet) stay on the maintainer's machine and get
# rsync'd to the server out-of-band.
**/*keypair*.json
**/*-key*.json
**/devnetkeypair.json

# Worker runtime state: contributions lists, vanity grinds, presale snapshots,
# spend history sqlite, etc. These contain wallet addresses & in some cases
# raw private keys (drill-keys, vanity-grind). Treat the whole dir as private.
pobindex-worker/data/

# ── Build artefacts ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
*.log
.vite/

# Anchor / Rust
staking-program/target/
staking-program/.anchor/
staking-program/test-ledger/
Cargo.lock

# ── OS / editor noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~
